%% Diagram: Architecture Decision Record lifecycle — from problem identification through options analysis and peer review to a versioned, searchable decision log
flowchart TD
    A["Architecture\nChallenge"]:::kv-primary --> B["Context &\nConstraints"]:::kv-highlight
    B --> C["Options\nAnalysis"]:::kv-accent
    C --> D["ADR\nDocument"]:::kv-accent
    D -->|"team review"| E{"Accepted?"}:::kv-outline
    E -->|"Yes"| F["Archived\nin Repository"]:::kv-primary
    E -->|"No"| C
    F --> G["Implementation\nTracking"]:::kv-highlight
    G -->|"superseded?"| A
